      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. i want to get even more specific with the \"vibe\" of the people in the scene to really drive home that sense of danger. when the protagonist is walking through, what kind of people are they seeing on the sidewalks or leaning against the buildings? give me some specific visual details about their appearance, what they're wearing, and how they carry themselves so i can tell my actors exactly what the energy should be.",
